data.name: textBox7.Text
data.value: Military Grid Reference System Reference https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_Grid_Reference_System Leading zeroes required for UTM Grid. Arbitrary precision may be entered for Easting and Northing, trailing zeroes are not required. Polar grids UTM grids A/B and Y/Z are not supported.

data.name: textBox9.Text
data.value: Universal Transverse Mercator Reference: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universal_Transverse_Mercator_coordinate_system Decimal values are allowed for easting and northing. Unit is meter. Polar grids UTM grids A/B and Y/Z are not supported.

data.name: label19.Text
data.value: Shift/Ctrl + Click to select multiple rows. Press delete to delete all selected rows. Press space to toggle import for all selected rows. Click XFER header to toggle all. Click Del header to delete all. Double click or enter to bring it over for editing.
